MALACANANG RESIDENCE OF THE PRESIDENT OF THE PHILIPPINES MANILA

PROCLAMATION NO. 827

EXCLUDING FROM THE OPERATION OF THE DAVAO PENAL COLONY RESERVATION SITUATED IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF STO. TOMAS, PROVINCE OF DAVAO DEL NORTE, ISLAND OF MINDANAO, A CERTAIN PORTION OF THE LAND EMBRACED THEREIN AND RESERVING THE SAME FOR SETTLEMENT PURPOSES UNDER THE ADMINISTRATION AND DISPOSITION OF THE LAND AUTHORITY.

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Agriculture and Natural Resources and pursuant to the authority vested in me by law, I, FERDINAND E. MARCOS, President of the Philippines, do hereby exclude from the operation of the Davao Penal Colony Reservation situated in the municipality of Sto. Tomas, province of Davao del Norte, island of Mindanao, a certain portion of the land embraced therein and reserve the same for settlement purposes under the administration and disposition of the Land Authority, subject to private rights, if any there be, and to future survey , which portion is more particularly described as follows:

LOGAN AREA Lot 4710 (Portion), Tagum Cad. 276

A parcel of land (Lot 4710 (portion), Tagum Cad. 276) and a portion of the Davao Penal Colony Reservation, situated at Barrio La Libertad, Santo Tomas, Davao, bounded on the North by Pls-424-D and Kapalong Cad. 284, on the East by the Davao Penal Colony Reservation, the South and West by the Davao Penal Colony Reservation and the Tuganay River, on the West by the Tuganay River and the Tanglaw Settlement (Gas-289). Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan being S. 51 deg . 28’E., 3224.77 meters from BBM No. 19 of Tagum Cad. 276,

